{"tid":1321080,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［前線入]對於Gear有少少建議","createTime":"2019-07-15T14:35:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T14:03:36.000Z","uid":18648,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"25bbd7ad8156f1230ea845989e454f7be1cef86a","tid":1321080,"uid":18648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:35:42.000Z","msg":"狗頭出晒口術<br />\n721好大機會出水炮車<br />\n再者出真係唔出奇<br />\n金鐘地闊居民少<br />\n<br />\n襯仲有五六日時間<br />\n我建議大家買返個<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">護陰罩</span></span><br />\n前線比人打春袋真係見唔少<br />\n比水炮車射中更加唔講得笑<br />\n中咗想走都要夾住春袋走 <br />\n傷害太大<br />\n<br />\n所以721上前線嘅 <br />\n盡可能係哩幾日時間<br />\n買返個護陰罩<br />\n<br />\n提提大家<br />\n小弟打開手球做龍門<br />\n屋企有一個<br />\n建議大家<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好買太緊</span></span><br />\n大脾會好痛<br />\n<br />\n有米嘅買多兩個<br />\n到時派比前線用<br />\n無米嘅自比自己就夠<br />\n今次一定要夠裝備保護自己<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔可以睇少水炮車嘅威力</span></span><br />\n補條link比手足睇下<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.gojns.com/taekwondo/groin-guard\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gojns.com%2Ftaekwondo%2Fgroin-guard&d=VPbJsUOTS2%2BU35Cb01K8cEXxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=dae98b39\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.gojns.com/taekwondo/groin-guard</a><br />\n<br />\n如果唔夠時間送到<br />\n可以試下踩上打拳或手球專門店問下<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">手足們 萬事小心<br />\n每個前線都好珍貴<br />\n我好愛你地</span>"},{"pid":"ceb0de5528ce75ae2ebbe9052c56dab6e05b1bfe","tid":1321080,"uid":140354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:36:43.000Z","msg":"有用POST, 推"},{"pid":"132709270a79a96ec38d6e040d83c68d72ff9da0","tid":1321080,"uid":24335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:37:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"374b2d72f39532af9071dc26be2c5d38a0027075","tid":1321080,"uid":6674,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:37:38.000Z","msg":"我都建議大家買套甲，